<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/27470888-cool-breeze"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1445866127i/27470888._UY100_CR16,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/27470888-cool-breeze">cool breeze</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">As stupid as it sounds (and is), there are plenty of idiots arguing that global warming causes earthquakes and tsunamis:<br/><br/><a href='http://www.theguardian.com/environment/2012/feb/26/why-climate-change-shake-earth' rel='nofollow noopener'>Climate change will shake the </a><a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">As stupid as it sounds (and is), there are plenty of idiots arguing that global warming causes earthquakes and tsunamis:<br /><br /><a href="http://www.theguardian.com/environment/2012/feb/26/why-climate-change-shake-earth" rel="nofollow noopener">Climate change will shake the Earth</a> (The Guardian)<br /><a href="http://www.newsweek.com/nepal-earthquake-could-have-been-manmade-disaster-climate-change-brings-326017" rel="nofollow noopener">More Fatal Earthquakes to Come, Geologists Warn</a> (Newsweek)<br /><a href="http://e360.yale.edu/feature/could_a_changing_climate_set_off_volcanoes_and_quakes/2525/" rel="nofollow noopener">Waking The Giant: How a Changing Climate Triggers Earthquakes, Tsunamis and Volcanoes</a> (Yale)<br /><br />Global warming - is there anything it can't do?<br />"Global warming turned me into a newt! (I got better)"<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
